{"type":"text","timestamp":1782368247917,"sessionID":"ses_10293461bffeeWYRBGoTh3K6fq","part":{"id":"prt_efd6d194e001KyBHU1fAXCNDU2","messageID":"msg_efd6d0cee001MJRibjF5Sd18J8","sessionID":"ses_10293461bffeeWYRBGoTh3K6fq","type":"text","text":"日志里真实问题是 `entry` combined module 与 `app/features.*` 之间的循环依赖，不是那条 experimental warning 本身。我先读取当前计划文件和相关 target 模块的导入关系，缩小到最小可修复范围。","time":{"start":1782368246094,"end":1782368247915}}}
