{"type":"text","timestamp":1782368366757,"sessionID":"ses_10293461bffeeWYRBGoTh3K6fq","part":{"id":"prt_efd6ee7dd001pKFHKwZEBlCZSs","messageID":"msg_efd6ed75f0016wSTaRIuXjWzou","sessionID":"ses_10293461bffeeWYRBGoTh3K6fq","type":"text","text":"循环依赖已清掉，构建推进到了真正的 Cangjie 语法错误：`bootstrap_page.cj` 的 `.padding({ ... })` 写法无效。现在查项目内已有 ArkUI/Cangjie 正确写法，做同类最小修复。","time":{"start":1782368364509,"end":1782368366756}}}
