onyos-6.1-8k\",\r\n      \"doc_kind\": \"overview\"\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"doc_id\": \"doc.harmonyos-6-1-8k-api-arkui-cj-cj-universal-attribute-imageeffect-overview-3\",\r\n      \"title\": \"示例代码\",\r\n      \"score\": 84.711,\r\n      \"summary\": \"本目录包含使用仓颉语言在ArkUI框架中进行UI开发和图像处理的代码示例集合。内容涵盖了基础的图片视觉属性设置（如模糊、阴影、色彩滤镜）以及高级的图像变化与渲染特效（如混合模式、离屏渲染、像素扩展）。这些示例旨在帮助开发者掌握HarmonyOS应用中的UI样式美化与渲染优化技巧，适用于希望提升应用视觉表现力的ArkUI开发者及测试人员。 - 你想学习基础的图片视觉属性设置吗？\",\r\n      \"paths\": [\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-universal-attribute-imageeffect/图像效果/示例代码/.overview.md\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"source\": \"harmonyos-6.1-8k\",\r\n      \"doc_kind\": \"overview\"\r\n    }\r\n  ],\r\n  \"paths\": [\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-universal-attribute-imageeffect/图像效果/示例代码/示例2设置图片不同变化效果/示例2设置图片不同变化效果_2.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-image-video-image/Image/示例代码/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-image-video-image/Image/示例代码/示例8设置SVG图片的填充颜色_0312600c.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-universal-attribute-imageeffect/图像效果/示例代码/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/Guide/media/image/cj-image-decoding/使用ImageSource完成图片解码/开发示例-对资源文件中的图片进行解码_0c78a17b.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-image-video-image/Image/组件属性/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-image-video-image/.abstract.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-image-video-image/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-image-video-image/Image/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-image-video-image/Image/基础类型定义/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/Guide/arkui-cj/cj-graphics-display/显示图片Image/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/Guide/arkui-cj/cj-graphics-display/显示图片Image/添加属性/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-animation-animation/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-animation-geometrytransition/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-animation-pagetransition/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-animation-sharedtransition/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-animation-transition/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/Guide/arkui-cj/cj-animation-smoothing/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/Guide/arkui-cj/cj-animation-smoothing/动画衔接/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/Guide/arkui-cj/cj-animation/.overview.md\"\r\n  ]\r\n}\r\n","exit":0,"description":"Searches AppResource examples","truncated":false},"title":"Searches AppResource examples","time":{"start":1782368454537,"end":1782368454556}},"id":"prt_efd7044da001osTu00MCLmDivX","sessionID":"ses_10293461bffeeWYRBGoTh3K6fq","messageID":"msg_efd70251e00136X4Maq8OQr7fn"}}
